y%20for%20scams%2C%20with%20%2410%20billion%20in%20losses%20reported%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EABA's%20proposed%20measures%20include%20a%20national%20strategy%2C%20new%20federal%20offices%2C%20and%20updated%20fraud%20laws.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20Spider-Man%20meme%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-posts-spiderman-meme-first-tweet-in-a-decade-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20points%20at%20himself%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Banks%20and%20the%20federal%20government%20are%20in%20a%20similar%20situation%2C%20pointing%20to%20each%20other%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20online%20financial%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20the%20government%20wants%20banks%20to%20take%20on%20more%20responsibility%2C%20and%20more%20consistently%20refund%20their%20customers%20who%20fall%20victim%20to%20online%20scams.%20Banks%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20want%20the%20government%20to%20do%20more%20to%20prevent%20those%20scams%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20real.%20Almost%201%20in%203%20Americans%20have%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20scam%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20with%20an%20average%20loss%20of%20%241%2C600%20a%20person%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20from%20IPX%2C%20a%20financial%20analysis%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20consumers%20reported%20more%20than%20%2410%20billion%20in%20losses%20last%20year%20from%20online%20scams.%20The%20agency's%20data%20also%20showed%20that%20consumers%20using%20payment%20apps%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-bill-zelle-fraud-payment-app-waters-blumenthal-warren-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elosing%20%24210%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20major%20headache%20for%20the%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Bankers%20Association%20CEO%20Rob%20Nichols%20called%20for%20the%20federal%20governmen