ch%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20starts%20at%20the%20very%20top.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20create%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20crimes%20intelligence%20centers.%26quot%3B%20One%20already%20exists%20in%20Texas%2C%20which%20he%20said%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bforce%20multiplier%20for%20law%20enforcement%26quot%3B%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENichols%20also%20called%20on%20the%20FTC%20to%20create%20a%20database%20of%20reported%20spam%20text%20messages%20available%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20legitimate%20businesses%20to%20access.%26quot%3B%20Nichols%20said%20this%20kind%20of%20database%20would%20help%20banks%20monitor%20how%20scams%20are%20evolving%20and%20%26quot%3Beducate%20their%20customers%26quot%3B%20more%20effectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-scams-fraud-liability-banks-government-ftc-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730672064000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723ea0401ea6d83dee586c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-scams-fraud-liability-banks-government-ftc-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Banks%20and%20the%20federal%20government%20are%20debating%20the%20best%20way%20to%20address%20rampant%20online%20scams%2C%20which%20have%20led%20to%20billions%20in%20losses%20for%20consumers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-scams-fraud-liability-banks-government-ftc-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20US%20is%20bracing%20for%20civil%20unrest%20around%20the%20election.%20But%20just%20how%20high%20is%20the%20risk%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fencing%20and%20other%20security%20barriers%20are%20going%20up%20around%20the%20US%20Capitol%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67279baa88cea3ba1c1dfe85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOfficials%20are%20preparing%20for%20potential%20civil%20unrest%20postelection.%3Cp%3EJ.%20Scott%20Applewhite%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20United%20States%20is%20preparing%20for%20civil%20unrest%20surrounding%20the%20election.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElection%20Day%20itself%20isn't%20as%20high%20of%20a%20risk%20as%20the%20postelection%20period%2C%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%202022%20midterms%20passed%20peacefully%2C%20tensions%20are%20higher%20during%20a%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20turmoil%20that%20took%20place%20after%20the%20last%20US%20presidential%20election%20has%20left%20its%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20time%20around%2C%20as%20Election%20Day%20looms%2C%20businesses%20and%20governments%20around%20the%20country%20are%20preparing%20in%20advance%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20the%20results%20are%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consensus%20going%20into%20Election%20Day%20is%20that%20will%20be%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-trump-presidential-election-swing-state-polls-sun-belt-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeven%20swing%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20offer%20multiple%20avenues%20for%20each%20candidate%20to%20win.%20And%20the%20final%20polls%20have%20largely%20shown%20the%20race%20between%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20a%20virtual%20tie%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlen%20Kucera%2C%20an%20executive%20at%20Allied%20Universal%2C%20a%20private%20security%20company%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20clientele%20are%20concerned%20enough%20to%20seek%20more%20resources%20to%20protect%20themselves%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20threat%20is%20kind%20of%20imminent%20and%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Kucera%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20the%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20stretch%20before%20Election%20Day%2C%20it%20seems%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elike%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eeveryone%20%E2%80%94%20from%20voter%20advocacy%20groups%20and%20election%20officials%20to%20risk%20management%20and%20security%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20is%20preparing%20for%20civil%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20is%20also%20now%20on%20people's%20minds%20is%20the%20emotion%2C%20the%20anger%20that%20goes%20with%20some%20of%20these%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Kucera%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20being%20deployed%20to%20try%20to%20figure%20all%20those%20imminent%20threats%20out%20and%20try%20to%20protect%20the%20public%20as%20we%20go%20into%20this%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20how%20high%20is%20the%20risk%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f2d6248-0787-4c0f-9dc3-5d53c2aad9c9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EElection%20Day%20isn't%20the%20biggest%20worry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElection%20Day%20itself%20isn't%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20most%20high-risk%20day%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunrest%20because%20there%20will%20be%20extensive%20protective%20measures%20taken%2C%20said%20Rachel%20Brown%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20violence%2C%20hate%20speech%2C%20and%20civic%20engagement%20at%20Over%20Zero%2C%20which%20works%20to%20deter%20identity-based%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20expect%20us%20to%20see%20a%20high%20level%20of%20organized%20violence.%20People%20should%20feel%20safe%20voting%2C%20and%20if%20there%20is%20any%20danger%2C%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20very%20highly%20localized%2C%20such%20as%20a%20single%20person%20taking%20action%20where%20there%20seem%20to%20be%20groups%20trying%20to%20mobilize%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said%20on%20Friday%20at%20a%20press%20panel%20hosted%20by%20the%20National%20Task%20Force%20on%20Election%20Crises%20(NTFEC)%2C%20a%20cross-partisan%20election%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20case%20in%20Washington%20and%20Oregon%2C%20where%20authorities%20are%20searching%20for%20what%20they%20say%20is%20a%20lone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eactor%20responsible%20for%20placing%20incendiary%20devices%20on%20at%20least%20two%20ballot%20drop%20boxes%2C%20burning%20hundreds%20of%20ballots.%20Officials%20in%20Clark%20County%2C%20Washington%2C%20where%20some%20488%20ballots%20were%20damaged%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20they%20have%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20voters%20affected%20to%20issue%20them%20replacement%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20ballot%20box%20was%20damaged%20in%20Multnomah%20County%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67279c4f88cea3ba1c1dfe89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20ballot%20box%20was%20damaged%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon.%3Cp%3EJenny%20Kane%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20protections%20in%20place%20for%20the%20voting%20process%2C%20voters%2C%20and%20election%20workers%2C%20Brown%20said.%20Voter%20intimidation%20is%20criminal%20and%20prosecutable%2C%20and%20locally%2C%20voting%20sites%20are%20preparing%20for%20any%20incidents%2C%20including%20swatting%20attacks%2C%20where%20a%20fake%20call%20is%20made%20to%20law%20enforcement%20to%20trigger%20an%20armed%20response%2C%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20threats%20that%20many%20of%20us%20aren't%20even%20thinking%20about%20day%20to%20day%2C%20election%20officials%20are%20working%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20to%20prevent%20and%20then%20respond%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Crawford%2C%20an%20NTFEC%20staffer%20and%20policy%20strategist%20at%20Protect%20Democracy%2C%20said%20at%20the%20panel.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20remedies%20when%20activities%20like%20this%20arise%20that%20election%20officials%20can%20still%20try%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20person%20can%20have%20their%20votes%20submitted%20and%20counted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20greater%20risk%20is%20likely%20postelection%2C%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-kamala-harris-preparing-legal-challenges-election-decided-court-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%20may%20be%20decided%20in%20courts%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20on%20election%20night.%20Then%2C%20there's%20the%20waiting%20game%20until%20Congress%20counts%20the%20electoral%20votes%20on%20January%206%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Presidential%20Inauguration%20Ceremony%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bmost%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20spike%20in%20conspiracy%20theories%20and%20threats%20to%20state%20capitals%2C%20vote%20count%20locations%2C%20and%20the%20individuals%20who%20oversee%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20such%20unrest%20after%20the%20election%2C%20businesses%20in%20Portland%20and%20other%20cities%20have%20begun%20boarding%20up%20their%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BViolence%20tends%20to%20happen%20to%20target%20the%20process%20and%20to%20contest%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20the%20dates%20that%20are%20relevant%20in%20the%20process%20and%20are%20able%20to%20anticipate%20where%20that%20might%20happen%2C%20but%20in%20a%20close%20election%2C%20we%20could%20see%20the%20use%20of%20violence%20or%20intimidation%20to%20attempt%20to%20sway%20how%20the%20results%20are%20processed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239042411-d542-4c03-b120-8bb15025a411%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20great%20is%20the%20risk%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVerisk%2C%20a%20data%20analytics%20and%20risk%20management%20company%2C%20ranked%20the%20United%20States%20among%20the%20five%20most%20high-risk%20countries%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20civil%20unrest%2C%20which%20could%20also%20lead%20to%20extensive%20insured%20losses%2C%20in%20the%20next%20year.%20Brazil%2C%20Colombia%2C%20Chile%2C%20and%20South%20Africa%20rounded%20out%20the%20list%2C%20with%20France%2C%20Greece%2C%20and%20Spain%20the%20riskiest%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerisk%20wrote%20in%20an%20October%20analysis%20that%20election-related%20violence%20is%20rare%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20that%20the%20January%206%20riot%20in%202021%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20standout%20protest%20event%20in%20US%20history.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20said%20the%20peaceful%202022%20midterm%20elections%20showed%20that%20the%20threat%20of%20civil%20violence%20remained%20comparatively%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmotions%20run%20higher%20during%20presidential%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20Strikes%20Riots%20and%20Civil%20Commotion%20Predictive%20Model%20found%20that%20the%20tension%20and%20political%20polarization%20could%20reach%20a%20boiling%20point%2C%20sparking%20unrest%20in%20urban%20centers%20like%20New%20York%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Chicago%2C%20and%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20is%20the%20underlying%20SRCC%20risk%20higher%20than%20in%20January%202021%2C%20the%20potential%20for%20flashpoints%20to%20ignite%20civil%20unrest%20is%20also%20greater%2C%26quot%3B%20Torbjorn%20Soltvedt%2C%20principal%20analyst%20at%20Verisk%20Maplecroft%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Munks%2C%20Verisk's%20head%20of%20research%20for%20the%20Americas%2C%20said%20that%20risks%20may%20also%20rise%20following%20the%20election%20during%20the%20certification%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrucially%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20election-related%20unrest%20will%20rise%20substantially%20if%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%20is%20tightly%20contested%2C%26quot%3B%20Munks%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20should%20Trump%20lose%20to%20Harris.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-civil-unrest-risk-kamala-harris-donald-trump-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730671860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67279bbe192f52589855c292%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-civil-unrest-risk-kamala-harris-donald-trump-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emotions%20are%20heightened%20ahead%20of%20Election%20Day%2C%20and%20they%20might%20remain%20so%20after%20the%20election%2C%20when%20analysts%20say%20the%20risk%20for%20civil%20unrest%20is%20higher.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-civil-unrest-risk-kamala-harris-donald-trump-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Queen%20Letizia%20in%20tears%20on%20visit%20to%20flood-hit%20Valencia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730670172000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F6fe7%2Flive%2Fe459db20-9a2b-11ef-82c3-45a801b7330b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc99rpd9kepxo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20anger%20flared%20in%20the%20stricken%20town%20of%20Paiporta%2C%20the%20Queen%20of%20Spain%2C%20with%20mud%20smeared%20on%20her%20face%2C%20was%20seen%20crying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc99rpd9kepxo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ariana%20Grande%26nbsp%3BGets%20Why%26nbsp%3B%E2%80%98Wicked%E2%80%99%20Fans%26nbsp%3BAre%20Nervous%20About%20Her%20Casting%3A%20As%20a%20Fan%