.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESherwin-Williams%20will%20join%20the%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20on%20November%208.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESherwin-Williams%20has%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20%2490.15%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20everything%20to%20know%20about%20the%20paint%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20neighborhood%20paint%20company%20just%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-dow-jones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20stock%20market%20indexes.%20It%20includes%2030%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20and%20capitalized%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Dow%20Jones%20Indices%20announced%20on%20Friday%20that%20it%20will%20add%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fshw-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESherwin-Williams%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20index%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20a%20more%20representative%20exposure%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20materials%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paint%20company%20will%20replace%20Dow%20Inc.%2C%20a%20materials%20science%20company%2C%20before%20trading%20opens%20on%20November%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Sherwin-Williams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c5ff687-9825-4fd9-8d54-3e4d256af199%5C%22%3EAll%20about%20The%20Sherwin-Williams%20Company%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201866%20by%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHenry%20Sherwin%20and%20Edward%20Williams%2C%20the%20company%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Cleveland%20and%20employs%20over%2064%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESherwin-Williams%20boasts%20of%20several%20innovations%20in%20the%20painting%20industry%2C%20including%20the%20first%20resealabl