ennsylvania%2C%20the%20most%20important%20swing%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20would%20win%20the%20race%20by%20holding%20the%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Wall%2C%26quot%3B%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Michigan%2C%20and%20the%20so-called%20Blue%20Dot%2C%20Nebraska's%202nd%20Congressional%20District.%20In%20that%20scenario%2C%20Trump%20could%20sweep%20the%20remaining%20four%20swing%20states%20and%20still%20fall%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20Trump%20wins%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Harris%20would%20be%20in%20a%20bind.%20If%20Harris%20won%20Michigan%20and%20Wisconsin%2C%20she%20would%20still%20need%20to%20add%20Georgia%20or%20North%20Carolina%20to%20her%20column.%20Even%20winning%20Michigan%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20Nevada%2C%20and%20Arizona%20would%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20put%20her%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20spend%20significant%20time%20in%20North%20Carolina%20looms%20large.%20He's%20set%20to%20spend%20the%20second-most%20time%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20campaign's%20final%20days%2C%20trailing%20only%20Pennsylvania.%20Harris%20held%20a%20rally%20in%20Charlotte%20on%20Saturday%20before%20flying%20to%20New%20York%20to%20make%20a%20surprise%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night%20Live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20polling%20aggregators%20show%20Trump%20with%20just%20over%20a%20one%20percentage%20point%20lead%20in%20the%20Tar%20Heel%20state.%20Despite%20President%20Obama%20being%20the%20only%20Democratic%20presidential%20hopeful%20to%20carry%20the%20state%20since%202000%2C%20Trump%20only%20narrowly%20held%20off%20President%20Biden%20there%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Harris'%20aides%20mocked%20Trump's%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20is%20worried%20about%20losing%20North%20Carolina%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20spokesperson%20Ammar%20Moussa%20wrote%20on%20X%20under%20two%20siren%20emojis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Sosnik%2C%20a%20longtime