etween%20our%20loan's%20interest%20and%20the%20interest%20paid%20on%20cash%20at%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20we%20just%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20what%20happens%20at%20the%20next%20Fed%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmortgage-rates-influence-when-we-pay-off-mortgage-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730647681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F620fa48ef0b06900185e8062%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmortgage-rates-influence-when-we-pay-off-mortgage-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20always%20wanted%20to%20pay%20off%20her%20mortgage%20early%2C%20but%20the%20math%20hasn't%20worked.%20But%20if%20mortgage%20rates%20fall%20after%20the%20Fed%20cut%20interest%20rates%2C%20it%20could.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Chamaa)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmortgage-rates-influence-when-we-pay-off-mortgage-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20India%20Is%20Disappearing%20Under%20China%20In%20Tectonic%20Tug-Of-War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20stand-off%20between%20India%20and%20China%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20found%20an%20amicable%20solution%20recently.%20However%2C%20another%20kind%20of%20tug-of-war%20between%20India%20and%20China%20-%20a%20continuous%20and%20ancient%20tectonic%20one%20-%20has%20been%20going%20on%20with%20the%20Indian%20tectonic%20plate%20constantly%20losing%20land%20by%20sliding%20under%20the%20Tibetan%20plate.%20The%20Indian%20landmass%20has%20been%20shrinking%20as%20its%20tectonic%20plate%20has%20been%20sliding%20under%20the%20Eurasian%20or%20Tibetan%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20correspondent%20experienced%20the%20war%20of%20continents%20first-hand%20high%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20at%20Hanle%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20where%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years%20or%20so%20Hanle%20may%20have%20risen%20by%20about%202.5%20centimetres%20since%20this%20correspondent's%20last%20visit%20almost%20a%20quarter%20century%20ago%20to%20the%20same%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20quirk%20of%20geological%20history%2C%20the%20Indian%20landmass%20is%20subducting%20or%20slipping%20under%20the%20Tibetan%20of%20the%20Asian%20landmass%20mainly%20comprising%20the%20current%20geographical%20area%20of%20China.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20reason%20the%20Himalayas%20-%20considered%20the%20ever-growing%20and%20youngest%20mountains%20-%20keep%20rising%205%20millimetres%20per%20year.%20The%20height%20of%20Mount%20Everest%2C%20too%2C%20keeps%20going%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pull%20and%20tug%20below%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20in%20northern%20India%20below%20the%20Himalayas%20is%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20earthquakes%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region.%20As%20the%20Indian%20plate%20slides%20below%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%2C%20steadily%20tension%20is%20built%20up%20almost%20like%20slow%20tightening%20of%20rubber%20band%2C%20then%20there%20comes%20a%20point%20when%20the%20taut%20tension%20is%20released%20as%20the%20ground%20gives%20way%2C%20leading%20to%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20region%20have%20not%20faced%20a%20mega-earthquake%20in%20more%20than%20500%20year%2C%20and%20some%20say%20a%20mega-earthquake%20is%20long%20overdue%20in%20the%20region.%20Experts%20say%20one%20can%20only%20build%20more%20resilient%20and%20earthquake-resistant%20structures%20to%20save%20lives%20since%20earthquakes%20cannot%20be%20stopped%20or%20even%20forecast%20as%20of%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tug-of-war%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20the%20Tibetan%20plates%20has%20its%20origins%20in%20a%20phenomenon%20called%20continental%20drift%2C%20which%20started%20almost%2060-70%20million%20years%20ago%3B%20it's%20also%20often%20called%20the%20'mega%20breakup'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Furu9t0dg_pallav-bagla_625x300_03_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20Science%20Editor%20Pallava%20Bagla%20at%20the%20site%20in%20Ladakh's%20Hanle%20where%20he%20saw%20the%20tectonic%20tug-of-war%20first-hand%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20landmass%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20supercontinent%20called%20'Gondwanaland'%2C%20which%20was%20situated%20close%20to%20the%20African%20continent.%20Because%20of%20the%20little-understood%20tectonic%20drama%2C%20the%20Indian%20plate%20started%20moving%20northwards%20and%20for%20a%20long%20time%20remained%20like%20an%20ever%20floating%20and%20mobile%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20at%20some%20point%2010-15%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Indian%20plate%20crashed%20into%20the%20Asian%20plate.%20This%20resulted%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20mountain%20range%20to%20be%20formed.%20Since%20then%20the%20Indian%20plate%20is%20gently%20but%20firmly%20being%20squeezed%20and%20swallowed%20under%20the%20Tibetan%20plate%20at%20the%20rate%20of%205%20to%206%20centimetres%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20accurately%20monitor%20what%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20Indian%20scientists%20from%20the%20CSIR%20Fourth%20Paradigm%20Institute%20(CSIR-4PI)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20have%20set%20up%20high-accuracy%20reference%20stations%20one%20on%20the%20Tibetan%20plate%20at%20Hanle%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20the%20other%20at%20Bengaluru.%20By%20tracking%20the%20movement%20of%20these%20reference%20points%20using%20sophisticated%20global%20positioning%20system%20(GPS)%20instruments%20and%20satellites%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20can%20assess%20how%20the%20land%20masses%20have%20moved%20respective%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20these%20last%2025%20years%2C%20Hanle%20has%20moved%20by%20almost%2085%20centimetres%20northeastwards.%20And%20India%2C%20let%20us%20say%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20has%20moved%20forward%20by%201.37%20metres%20northeast.%20This%20movement%20causes%20stress%2C%20which%20manifests%20in%20earthquakes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Sridevi%20Jade%2C%20Director%2C%20CSIR%20Fourth%20Paradigm%20Institute%20(CSIR-4PI)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20a%20specialist%20on%20measuring%20the%20continental%20drift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saving%20grace%20though%2C%20as%20Dr%20Jade%20said%2C%20is%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20unlikely%20to%20disappear%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730647200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fe2rh4s98_hanle-ladakh_625x300_03_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-india-is-disappearing-under-china-in-tectonic-tug-of-war-6935701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20military%20stand-off%20between%20India%20and%20China%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20found%20an%20amicable%20solution%20recently.%20However%2C%20another%20kind%20of%20tug-of-war%20between%20India%20and%20China%20-%20a%20continuous%20and%20ancient%20tectonic%20one%20-%20has%20been%20going%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-india-is-disappearing-under-china-in-tectonic-tug-of-war-6935701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Severe%20storms%20ravage%20Oklahoma%3A%206%20injured%2C%20several%20homes%20damaged%3B%20thousands%20without%20power%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730647045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114915862%2Cimgsize-2250016.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsevere-storms-ravage-oklahoma-6-injured-several-homes-damaged-thousands-withou