s%20and%20protect%20these%20assets%20and%20the%20information%20that%20they%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db68d173-5635-4361-bd7d-f42450adf2ce%5C%22%3ECybersecurity%20demand%20isn't%20being%20met%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20there%20are%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20positions%20open%20here%20in%20North%20America%2C%20probably%20more%20than%20a%20million%20globally.%20As%20industry%20importance%20continues%20to%20rise%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybersecurity-jobs-openings-how-to-hire-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20talent%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20all%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we're%20seeing%20right%20now%20in%20the%20industry%20is%20that%20we%20can't%20bring%20folks%20in%20fast%20enough.%20That%20means%20we're%20a%20little%20bit%20behind%20in%20terms%20of%20filling%20the%20pipeline%20with%20viable%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20clear%20direct%20path%20into%20cybersecurity%20unless%20you%20are%20one%20of%20the%20rare%20people%20who%20has%20actually%20majored%20in%20the%20newly%20available%20cybersecurity%20majors%20in%20our%20educational%20system.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelax-college-kids-ai-will-not-kill-computer-science-degree-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EComputer%20science%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20been%20around%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20number%20of%20years%20but%20even%20that%20doesn't%20provide%20you%20a%20direct%20line%20to%20cyber%20security%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20cybersecurity%20professionals%20have%20started%20their%20careers%20as%20IT%20professionals%20and%20at%20some%20point%20transitioned%20over.%20But%2C%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20there%20still%20aren't%20enough%20people%20to%20feed%20the%20robust%20pipeline%20or%20open%20positions%20that%20we%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20a%20candidate%20would%20be%20someone%20that%20has%20done%20the%20academic%20work%20associated%20with%20it%20or%20they%20gained%20certifications%20across%20the%20cyber%20security%20spectrum%20and%20have%20combined%20some%20level%20of%20practical%20experience.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20ton%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20prejudice%20toward%20people%20who%20have%20hands-on%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20with%20our%20industry%20is%20that%20hands-on%20experience%20portion%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20challenge%20to%20get%20for%20new%20entrants.%20That's%20where%20the%20gap%20continues%20to%20increase%20in%20terms%20of%20available%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20industry%2C%20we%20have%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20and%20start%20planning%20and%20making%20changes%20so%20that%20we're%20prepared%20for%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%20next%20three%20to%20five%20years%2C%20which%20means%20we%20need%20to%20make%20an%20investment%20in%20that%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20team%20called%20Grow%20with%20Google%20and%20some%20of%20the%20other%20teams%20internally%20here%20that%20pay%20particular%20interest%20to%20what%20people%20need%20to%20learn%20in%20a%20future%20state%2C%20and%20we%20invest%20time%20in%20building%20out%20courses%2C%20certificates%2C%20and%20opportunities%20for%20people%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227f12508-6fec-4ba2-9215-0f451653a751%5C%22%3EIt's%20a%20field%20that's%20here%20to%20stay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-may-want-to-rethink-ai-career-path-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%20roles%20will%20continue%20to%20flourish%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20relevance%20for%20a%20decade-plus%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20even%20gotten%20to%20the%20point%20where%20we're%20talking%20about%20cryptographic%20challenges.%20In%20terms%20of%20post-quantum%20computing%2C%20cybersecurity%20is%20g