onse%20to%20the%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lt%20Governor%20spoke%20to%20DGP%20Nalin%20Prabhat%20and%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20security%20agencies%20on%20the%20grenade%20attack%20in%20Srinagar.%20He%20directed%20the%20security%20officials%20for%20an%20effective%20and%20forceful%20response%20to%20punish%20the%20terrorists%20and%20their%20associates.%20You%20have%20full%20freedom%20to%20crush%20terror%20outfits%20and%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20complete%20this%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sinha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Union%20Territory%2C%20security%20and%20law%20and%20order%20are%20under%20the%20central%20government%20and%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20-%20not%20the%20elected%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20few%20days%20have%20seen%20a%20series%20of%20gunfights%20between%20terrorists%20and%20security%20personnel.%20Yesterday%2C%20a%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%20terrorist%20was%20gunned%20down%20in%20Srinagar's%20Khanyar%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVidhi%20Kumar%20Birdi%2C%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20for%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20the%20terrorist%2C%20Usman%2C%20was%20a%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%20commander.%C2%A0%26quot%3BNow%20this%20operation%20has%20been%20completed.%20Security%20forces%20have%20killed%20a%20terrorist%2C%20who%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Usman...%2C%20he%20was%20the%20commander%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20and%204%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20injured.%20He%20is%20a%20foreign%20terrorist%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20yesterday%2C%20security%20forces%20gunned%20down%20two%20terrorists%20in%20an%20encounter%20in%20Anantnag%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730646480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fvmeojhog_srinagar-grenade-attack_625x300_03_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrenade-attack-at-sunday-market-in-j-ks-srinagar-at-least-6-injured-6933958%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20six%20people%20have%20been%20injured%20after%20terrorists%20threw%20a%20grenade%20at%20a%20Sunday%20market%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Srinagar.%20Six%20people%20have%20been%20rushed%20to%20hospital.%20More%20details%20are%20awaited.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrenade-attack-at-sunday-market-in-j-ks-srinagar-at-least-6-injured-6933958%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain's%20King%20And%20PM%20Attacked%20With%20Mud%20During%20Visit%20To%20Flood%20Hit%20Valencia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFurious%20locals%20pelted%20Spain's%20royals%20and%20premier%20on%20Sunday%20with%20mud%20and%20cries%20of%20%26quot%3Bmurderers!%26quot%3B%2C%20forcing%20officials%20to%20cut%20short%20their%20visit%20to%20the%20town%20worst%20hit%20by%20the%20floods%20which%20have%20killed%20more%20than%20200.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20angry%20crowd%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Paiporta%20focused%20most%20of%20its%20wrath%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Valencia%20region%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20whisked%20away%20by%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%20Felipe%20VI%20and%20Queen%20Letizia%20were%20hit%20in%20the%20face%20and%20clothes%20with%20mud%20as%20they%20tried%20to%20calm%20the%20angry%20crowd%2C%20AFP%20journalists%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBroadcast%20on%20Spanish%20television%2C%20the%20extraordinary%20scenes%20underscored%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20anger%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20response%20to%20the%20nation's%20worst%20such%20disaster%20in%20decades%2C%20with%20the%20toll%20ever%20rising%20and%20hopes%20for%20finding%20survivors%20ebbing%20five%20days%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20king%20and%20queen%20arrived%20just%20after%20midday%20at%20a%20crisis%20centre%20in%20Paiporta%2C%20ground%20zero%20for%20a%20disaster%20Sanchez%20called%20the%20second%20deadliest%20flood%20in%20Europe%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20security%20guards%20were%20soon%20called%20to%20stand%20between%20the%20royals%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20delegation%20and%20the%20angry%20crowd%2C%20whose%20ire%20seemed%20most%20directed%20at%20Sanchez%20and%20Valencia%20region%20head%20Carlos%20Mazon%2C%20AFP%20journalists%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sanchez%20and%20the%20politicians%20quickly%20left%2C%20the%20king%20and%20queen%20spent%20an%20hour%20trying%20to%20calm%20tempers%20before%20leaving%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20public%20television%20said%20that%20their%20visit%20to%20the%20flood-hit%20region%20had%20been%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20the%20flood%20deaths%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Valencia%20region%2C%20where%20Spain's%20meteorological%20agency%20on%20Sunday%20issued%20a%20fresh%20warning%20for%20heavy%20downpours%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20100%20litres%20per%20square%20metre%20(22%20gallons%20per%20square%20yard)%20of%20water%20could%20fall%20in%20places%20in%20the%20province%20of%20Castellon%20and%20the%20area%20surrounding%20the%20city%20of%20Valencia%2C%20the%20agency%20forecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20for%20torrential%20rain%20that%20may%20cause%20flooding%20in%20the%20southern%20province%20of%20Almeria%2C%20advising%20residents%20not%20to%20travel%20unless%20strictly%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Towns%20buried%20by%20mud'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Tuesday's%20torrent%20of%20rain%20and%20mud%20swept%20away%20vehicles%20and%20devastated%20towns%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20thousands%20of%20security%20and%20emergency%20services%20have%20frantically%20cleared%20debris%20and%20mud%20in%20the%20search%20for%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20come%20under%20fire%20over%20the%20warning%20systems%20before%20the%20floods%2C%20and%20stricken%20residents%20have%20complained%20that%20the%20response%20to%20the%20disaster%20has%20been%20too%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMazon%20himself%20has%20faced%20fierce%20criticism%20for%20waiting%20until%20Tuesday%20evening%20to%20issue%20a%20phone%20alert%20in%20Valencia%2C%20despite%20his%20region%20being%20under%20an%20extreme%20weather%20warning%20since%20that%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20aware%20the%20response%20is%20not%20enough%2C%20there%20are%20problems%20and%20severe%20shortages...%20towns%20buried%20by%20mud%2C%20desperate%20people%20searching%20for%20their%20relatives...%20we%20have%20to%20improve%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanchez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20torrents%20of%20muddy%20water%20having%20wrecked%20towns%20and%20swept%20away%20cars%2C%20restoring%20order%20and%20distributing%20aid%20to%20destroyed%20towns%20and%20villages%20--%20some%20of%20which%20have%20been%20cut%20off%20from%20food%2C%20water%20and%20power%20since%20Tuesday%20--%20is%20a%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Spain%20deploying%20an%20extra%2010%2C000%20troops%2C%20police%20and%20civil%20guards%20to%20the%20Valencia%20region%2C%20the%20country%20was%20carrying%20out%20its%20largest%20deployment%20of%20military%20and%20security%20force%20personnel%20in%20peacetime%2C%20Sanchez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20to%20the%20people%20who%20have%20come%20to%20help%20us%2C%20to%20all%20of%20them%2C%20because%20from%20the%20authorities%3A%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20furious%20Estrella%20Caceres%2C%2066%2C%20told%20AFP%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Sedavi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chiva%20Danna%20Daniella%20said%20she%20had%20been%20cleaning%20her%20restaurant%20for%20three%20days%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20was%20still%20in%20shock%2C%20haunted%20by%20memories%20of%20the%20people%20trapped%20by%20the%20raging%20floodwaters%20%26quot%3Basking%20for%20help%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20we%20could%20do%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20drives%20you%20crazy.%20You%20look%20for%20answers%20and%20you%20don't%20find%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Swiss%20cheese'%20motorways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20telephone%20and%20transport%20networks%20severely%20damaged%2C%20establishing%20a%20precise%20figure%20of%20missing%20people%20is%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransport%20Minister%20Oscar%20Puente%20told%20El%20Pais%20daily%20that%20certain%20places%20would%20probably%20remain%20inaccessible%20by%20land%20for%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrdinary%20citizens%20carrying%20food%2C%20water%20and%20cleaning%20equipment%20have%20continued%20their%20grassroots%20initiative%20to%20assist%20the%20recovery%2C%20although%20authorities%20have%20urged%20people%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20to%20avoid%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Valencian%20government%20limited%20the%20number%20of%20volunteers%20authorised%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20city's%20southern%20suburbs%20to%202%2C000%20and%20restricted%20access%20to%2012%20localities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20thousands%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Valencia's%20centre%20to%20make%20way%20to%20nearby%20communes%20on%20foot%2C%20carrying%20brooms%20and%20shovels%20to%20help%20those%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Pope%20Francis%20offered%20his%20prayers%20to%20those%20hit%20by%20the%20disaster%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20suffering%20so%20much%20these%20days%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20storm%20that%20sparked%20the%20floods%20on%20Tuesday%20formed%20as%20cold%20air%20moved%20over%20the%20warm%20waters%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20and%20is%20common%20for%20this%20time%20of%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20scientists%20warn%20climate%20change%20driven%20by%20human%20activity%20is%20increasing%20the%20ferocity%2C%20length%20and%20frequency%20of%20such%20extreme%20weather%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmergency%20services%20on%20Sunday%20updated%20the%20toll%20to%20217%20