0posed%20by%20stray%20dogs%20during%20the%20operation%20against%20Usman%2C%20a%20commander%20of%20the%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20concern%20was%20the%20presence%20of%20stray%20dogs%2C%20whose%20barking%20could%20potentially%20alert%20the%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20this%2C%20search%20teams%20were%20equipped%20with%20biscuits%20to%20soothe%20the%20dogs%20as%20they%20approached%20their%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20Usman%2C%20who%20was%20well%20familiar%20with%20the%20Valley%20terrain%2C%20was%20a%20significant%20figure%20in%20orchestrating%20numerous%20terror%20attacks%20since%20his%20initial%20activity%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20stint%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20he%20infiltrated%20back%20into%20the%20region%20around%202016-17%20and%20was%20implicated%20in%20the%20shooting%20of%20police%20inspector%20Masroor%20Wani%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20intelligence%20indicated%20Usman's%20presence%20in%20a%20residential%20area%2C%20a%20meticulous%20nine-hour%20planning%20phase%20ensued%20to%20ensure%20the%20operation's%20success%20without%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20deployment%20was%20done%20before%20Fajar%20(pre-dawn%20prayers)%2C%20with%20security%20forces%20cordoning%20off%20a%20cluster%20of%2030%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20standoff%20escalated%20when%20Usman%20--%20armed%20with%20an%20AK-47%2C%20a%20pistol%2C%20and%20numerous%20grenades%20--%20engaged%20in%20a%20fierce%20gunfire%20exchange%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20confrontation%2C%20some%20grenades%20detonated%2C%20igniting%20a%20fire%20in%20the%20house%20that%20was%20quickly%20contained%20by%20the%20security%20personnel%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20spreading%20to%20nearby%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20hours%20of%20intense%20gunfire%2C%20Usman%20was%20neutralise