lations%20NZ%20you%20outplayed%20us.%20Been%20saying%20from%20many%20years.%20Team%20India%20needs%20to%20play%20on%20better%20pitches.%20These%20turning%20pitches%20making%20every%20batsman%20look%20very%20ordinary%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20generations%20batsmen%20never%20played%20on%20these%20kind%20of%20tracks.%20These%20tracks%20are%20prepared%20for%202%2F3%20day%20Test%20matches.%20You%20don't%20need%20Murli%2C%20Warne%20or%20Saqi%20on%20these%20pitches%20to%20get%20the%20teams%20out.%20Anyone%20can%20get%20anyone%20out.%26quot%3B%20Former%20all-rounder%20Irfan%20Pathan%20highlighted%20the%20lack%20of%20red-ball%20cricket%20for%20the%20senior%20India%20batters%20as%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20debacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20embarrassing%20display%20by%20team%20India%20at%20home.%20Lot%20to%20ponder%20over%20by%20the%20decision%20makers.%20Well%20done%20New%20Zealand%20on%20such%20a%20terrific%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20a%20solid%20conversation%20with%20%40iamyusufpathan%20bhai%20yesterday.%20He%20made%20a%20valid%20point%20about%20domestic%20cricket%20%E2%80%93%20we're%20either%20playing%20on%20grassy%20pitches%20or%20flat%20tracks%2C%20but%20rarely%20on%20turning%20surfaces%20anymore.%20Plus%2C%20top%20players%20aren't%20playing%20domestic%20cricket.%20This%20could%20hurt%20us%20in%20the%20long%20run.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20embarrassing%20display%20by%20team%20India%20at%20home.%20Lot%20to%20ponder%20over%20by%20the%20decision%20makers.%20Well%20done%20New%20Zealand%20on%20such%20a%20terrific%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Irfan%20Pathan%20(%40IrfanPathan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIrfanPathan%2Fstatus%2F1852977531516846484%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb