how%2F114913615.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eye%20On%20Purvanchali%20Vote%2C%20AAP%20Vs%20BJP%20Over%20Chhat%20Puja%20Ghat%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20festive%20season%20in%20Delhi%20appears%20to%20be%20headed%20for%20a%20contentious%20closure%20with%20a%20clash%20between%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20over%20the%20ghats%20for%20bathing%20during%20the%20coming%20Chhath%20puja.%20The%20parties%20have%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Banti-Purvanchali%26quot%3B%20and%20AAP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20police%20are%20deliberately%20closing%20down%20ghats%20and%20pushing%20around%20the%20poor%20who%20are%20waiting%20to%20celebrate%20Chhath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-day%20Chhath%20puja%20which%20started%20today%2C%20is%20the%20veneration%20of%20the%20sun.%20It%20is%20the%20biggest%20festival%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Jharkhand%20and%20is%20observed%20with%20enthusiasm%20by%20the%20migrant%20Bihari%20community%20across%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20also%20observed%20in%20parts%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20several%20ghats%20on%20the%20Yamuna%20and%20other%20water%20bodies%20are%20reserved%20for%20the%20devotees%2C%20who%20bath%20and%20make%20offerings%20both%20to%20the%20rising%20and%20setting%20sun.%20The%20trouble%20this%20time%20is%20over%20the%20Satpula%20ghat%20in%20south%20Delhi%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20traditional%20spot%20for%20Chhath%20puja.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20tension%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20AAP%20supporters%20and%20the%20police%20came%20in%20to%20restore%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20have%20resorted%20to%20full-scale%20hooliganism%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20told%20reporters%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20poor%2C%20particularly%20Dalits%2C%20are%20celebrating%20Chhath%20and%20the%20police%20are%20barricading%20the%20ghat%20so%20they%20can't%20celebrate.%20This%20is%20being%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20BJP's%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Shikha%20Rai%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20DDA%20group%20that%20has%20clearance%20to%20celebrate%20Chhath%2C%20are%20not%20being%20given%20access%20to%20the%20ghat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20have%20been%20here%20since%20yesterday%20disrupting%20construction%20work.%20The%20labourers%20are%20being%20beaten%20up...%20I%20don't%20understand%20--%20if%20you%20are%20anti-Hindu%2C%20anti-Purvanchali%2C%20why%20not%20just%20say%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20up%20tents%20and%20portable%20changing%20rooms%20and%20organising%20the%20space%20on%20the%20ghats%20are%20among%20the%20preparatory%20work%20for%20the%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20said%20they%20have%20sought%20clearance%20from%20the%20DDA%2C%20and%20the%20AAP%20claims%20that%20they%20have%20clearance%20from%20the%20Sub-Divisional%20Magistrate.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clash%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20Delhi%2C%20scheduled%20in%20February%20next%20year%2C%20and%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Purvanchali%20community%20would%20be%20crucial%20for%20both%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20Union%20minister%2C%20Late%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20and%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20the%20spot%20this%20evening.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730640180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F8qkdmk4g_chhath-ghat_625x300_03_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feye-on-purvanchali-vote-aap-vs-bjp-over-chhat-puja-ghat-in-delhi-6935267%22%2C%22summ