ne-news%2Fon-cctv-speeding-car-kills-man-bursting-crackers-on-road-in-pune-6935208%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BCCI%20To%20Take%20Big%20Step%20On%20Virat%2C%20Rohit%2C%20Jadeja%20And%20Ashwin%20-%20Report's%20Huge%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20of%20some%20senior%20India%20players%20will%20be%20decided%20after%20the%20tour%20of%20Australia%20as%20the%20BCCI%20evaluates%20the%20shocking%200-3%20drubbing%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%20while%20rolling%20out%20a%20structured%20phaseout%20policy%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20next%20WTC%20cycle.%20There%20is%20a%20high%20possibility%20that%20the%20five-match%20Test%20series%20against%20Australia%20could%20be%20the%20final%20one%20for%20at%20least%20two%20of%20the%20four%20seniors%20among%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20are%20in%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20their%20international%20careers.%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20can%20look%20that%20far%20ahead.%20It's%20important%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20next%20series%2C%20which%20is%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20when%20asked%20for%20his%20thoughts%20on%20India's%20Test%20future%20given%20there%20is%20limited%20time%20left%20in%20his%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20look%20beyond%20Australia%20series.%20Australia%20series%2C%20for%20us%20is%20now%20very%2C%20very%20important.%20We%20will%20try%20and%20focus%20on%20that%20rather%20than%20thinking%20what%20happens%20after%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20informal%20discussion%20could%20take%20place%20between%20BCCI%20bigwigs%20and%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20and%20skipper%20Rohit%20about%20the%20way%20forward%20for%20an%20ageing%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStocks%20will%20be%20taken%20certainly%20and%20it%20could%20be%20of%20informal%