rg%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkeep-kamala-and-carry-on-la-harris-makes-hilarious-appearance-on-sunday-night-live-watch-video%2Famp_articleshow%2F114903571.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkeep-kamala-and-carry-on-la-harris-makes-hilarious-appearance-on-sunday-night-live-watch-video%2Famp_articleshow%2F114903571.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Family%E2%80%99s%20Struggle%20is%20Changing%20Dialysis%20Care%20%26amp%3B%20Making%20It%20More%20Easily%20Available%20In%20Tier%202%20%26amp%3B%203%20Cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%20(CKD)%20and%20advised%20to%20start%20dialysis%2C%20the%20family%20faced%20a%20significant%20decision.%20Residing%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%20Prabhat%20was%20disappointed%20with%20the%20available%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336026%2Fdr-sudhir-srivastava-made-in-india-surgical-robot-cheaper-surgeries-affordable-healthcare-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20dialysis%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20hometown%20and%20encouraged%20his%20parents%20to%20move%20with%20him%20to%20Gurgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20relocation%20took%20a%20huge%20toll%20on%20the%20family%20and%20led%20to%20many%20conversations%20around%20the%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20good%20dialysis%20care%20in%20India.%20As%20Prabhat%20discussed%20this%20with%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20nephrologist%2C%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20had%20to%20address%20this%20gap.%20Another%20friend%20of%20Prabhat%E2%80%99s%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%2C%20a%20Chartered%20Accountant%2C%20joined%20them%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20make%20quality%20dialysis%20care%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20government%20report%2C%20over%202.2%20lakh%20patients%20are%20diagnosed%20with%20end-stage%20renal%20disease%20(ESRD)%20every%20year%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20demand%20of%203.4%20crore%20dialysis%20sessions%20annually.%20The%20challenge%20lies%20in%20the%20insufficient%20number%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20across%20the%20country.%20Prabhat%20states%20that%20while%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20dialysis%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20only%205%2C000%20exist%2C%20highlighting%20a%20critical%20need%20for%20more%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%20July%202017%2C%20VitusCare%20Medlife%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20towns.%20Over%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20they%20have%20established%2035%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20seven%20states%20across%20North%20India%2C%20providing%20over%2015%2C000%20sessions%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20idea%20was%20very%20clear%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20vision%20comes%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20united%20the%20three%20founders%20was%20their%20shared%20background%20from%20Tier%202%20cities.%20Prabhat%2C%20a%20lawyer%20from%20Jabalpur.%20Dr%20Saurabh%20from%20Dehradun%20with%2018%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20and%20Pankaj%20from%20Agra%2C%20a%20corporate%20finance%20expert%2C%20all%20recognised%20the%20pressing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333216%2Fiit-guwahati-invents-sensor-for-diabetes-diet-low-glycemic-index-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneed%20for%20better%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20his%20parents%20to%20Gurgaon%20in%202015%2C%20Prabhat%20started%20brainstorming%20possible%20