C%20the%20project%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20effort%20to%20rejuvenate%2065%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20employing%20treated%20wastewater%20and%20rainwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20project%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20involves%20reviving%20an%20old%20well%20and%20digging%20borewells%20to%20access%20the%20aquifer%2C%20along%20with%20the%20installation%20of%20water%20treatment%20plants%20in%20two%20phases.%20Now%2C%20the%20system%20provides%206.4%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20daily%2C%20helping%20supplement%20the%20domestic%20water%20requirement%20of%2045%2C000%20residents%20in%20Devanahalli.%20This%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20collaboration%20of%20many%20organisations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Carl%20Zeiss%2C%20Rotary%20South%20Parade%20Bangalore%2C%20and%20Wipro%20Foundation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20water%20crisis%20and%20lake%20rejuvenation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C40