20which%20means%20we%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20careful%20steps%20to%20maintain%20high%20water%20standards%20and%20an%20appropriate%20design.%20In%20terms%20of%20power%20usage%2C%20we%20cannot%20have%20a%20complex%2C%20elaborate%20treatment%20system%20that%20consumes%20a%20lot%20of%20power%20for%20water%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20use%20a%20few%20pumps%20to%20move%20water%20through%20the%20system%2C%20keeping%20power%20consumption%20low.%20Now%2C%20imagine%20if%20we%20had%20to%20use%20RO%20(reverse%20osmosis)%20and%20UF%20(ultrafiltration)%3B%20it%20would%20become%20too%20complex%20in%20terms%20of%20power%20requirements.%20Since%20the%20water%20from%20the%20well%20and%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20meets%20IS%2010500%20standards%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20treat%20it%20with%20a%20simple%20four-stage%20treatment%20process%20to%20ensure%20safety%2C%20making%20it%20suitable%20for%20domestic%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20S%2C%20a%20civil%20engineer%2C%20water%20management%20expert%20and%20advisor%20at%20Biome%20Environmental%20Trust%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CDevanahalli%20town%20relies%20heavily%20on%20deep%20borewells%20for%20its%20water%20supply.%20Through%20this%20project%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20revive%20the%20local%20lake%2C%20recharge%20groundwater%2C%20and%20explore%20how%20a%20town%20can%20become%20self-sufficient%20by%20using%20both%20local%20water%20sources%20and%20treated%20wastewater.%20The%20project%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20meet%20Devanahalli%E2%80%99s%205.4%20MLD%20(million%20litres%20per%20day)%20water%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5B1%20MLD%20(million%20litres%20per%20day)%20is%20equal%20to%201%2C000%20KLD%20